    <bodyBottom>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/64153924@N08/8634251644" target="_blank" data-v-e1c1f65a="">"Tuberculosis Research"</a> by <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/64153924@N08" target="_blank" data-v-e1c1f65a="">USAID Asia</a> is licensed under <a rel="noopener" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/2.0/?ref=ccsearch&amp;atype=rich" target="_blank" class="photo_license" data-v-e1c1f65a="">CC BY-NC 2.0</a></p>]]></Value>
